---
title: Peking Marinated Tofu & Garlic Rice Bowl with Crushed Peanuts & Soy Mayo
description: We love poke bowls, because they’re so easy to customise with your favourite flavours. This veggie version uses Peking-style tofu, Asian greens, carrot and cucumber, with a soy mayo to tie the whole thing together.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/peking-tofu-poke-bowl-8197b811.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipecards/card/peking-tofu-poke-bowl-5eb38a6300a80079c7570a78-fe1e9b48.pdf
